BT /F1 10 Tf 54 417.6 Td (Goal: Replace your $5,000/month salary) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 403.6 Td (If each property cash flows $400/month...) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 389.6 Td (You need: 13 properties = $5,200/month = FREEDOM) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 375.6 Td (Timeline: 5-10 years of consistent investing) Tj ET
