BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (CHAPTER 3: HOW TO FINANCE YOUR FIRST PROPERTY) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (FINANCING OPTIONS \(from easiest to hardest\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 650.4 Td (1. FHA LOAN \(3.5% down\) - Must live in property) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 636.4 Td (   Requirements: 580+ credit score, 2 years employment) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 622.4 Td (   Best for: House-hacking your first property) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.4 Td (   Example: $200K property = $7,000 down payment) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.6 Td (2. CONVENTIONAL LOAN \(15-25% down for investment\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.6 Td (   Requirements: 680+ credit, 6 months reserves) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.6 Td (   Best for: Properties you won't live in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.6 Td (   Example: $200K property = $40-50K down payment) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 518.8 Td (3. VA LOAN \(0% down\) - Veterans only) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 504.8 Td (   Requirements: Military service, COE) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 490.8 Td (   Best for: Veterans house-hacking \(up to 4 units!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 467.0 Td (4. HARD MONEY LOANS \(for flips\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 453.0 Td (   Requirements: Good deal \(they lend on the deal, not you\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 439.0 Td (   Rates: 10-15% interest, 1-3 points) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 425.0 Td (   Best for: Fix & flip with 6-12 month timeline) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 401.2 Td (5. SELLER FINANCING \(creative!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 387.2 Td (   Requirements: Motivated seller willing to 'be the bank') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.2 Td (   Best for: Off-market deals with flexible sellers) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 349.4 Td (6. PARTNERSHIPS / OPM \(Other People's Money\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 335.4 Td (   Structure: You find deals + manage, partner provides capital) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 321.4 Td (   Split: Typically 50/50 of profits) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 307.4 Td (   Best for: Experienced investors without liquid cash) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 279.6 Td (HOW TO GET YOUR CREDIT READY:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 263.6 Td ([ ] Check credit score \(free at annualcreditreport.com\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 249.6 Td ([ ] Pay down credit cards below 30% utilization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 235.6 Td ([ ] Don't open new accounts 6 months before applying) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 221.6 Td ([ ] Dispute any errors on your report) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 207.6 Td ([ ] Target: 700+ for best rates, 620+ minimum) Tj ET
endstream
